        <h2 class="section-title">30 Years Serving <span style="color:var(--red)">Vancouver</span></h2>
        <div class="divider"></div>
        <p style="color:var(--muted);line-height:1.8;margin-bottom:1rem;">Founded in 1994 by brothers Rick and Ali Habib, Fraserview Collision was built on one principle: every vehicle deserves the best possible repair, regardless of make or model. We treat your car — whether it's your family sedan, work van, or weekend SUV — like it's the most important vehicle in the shop.</p>
